<p><span style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;">For a century corporations have used the military and government of our country to make war on people around the world. They have done this for profit and without showing a shred of conscience.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;">Today, the world is fed up. If the roles were reversed, we would have taken action long since.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;">These same interests understand well Americans are waking from their long sleep. This why drone technologies are now being deployed within the United States.</span></p>
